{"tid":2136352,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"入境86天 台外籍工程師確診","createTime":"2020-08-02T05:47:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T06:14:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bedc9c26200775eeee8d1e871dbf018184b67a48","tid":2136352,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T05:47:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200802/VCNTFXXJVEJZ6F3GIXEZLTDDWI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200802%2FVCNTFXXJVEJZ6F3GIXEZLTDDWI%2F&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnYGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=350b7d9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200802%2FVCNTFXXJVEJZ6F3GIXEZLTDDWI%2F&h=3c480e74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200802/VCNTFXXJVEJZ6F3GIXEZLTDDWI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n入境86天 台外籍工程師確診<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/a81gBpr2s8DLG-l0XIL9QUUcVpU=/1103x577/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/37E5JP3RAGPQAX46UC6FGQH3RM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fa81gBpr2s8DLG-l0XIL9QUUcVpU%3D%2F1103x577%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F37E5JP3RAGPQAX46UC6FGQH3RM.gif&h=85c2188d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣武漢肺炎疫情逾110日無本土確診個案恐破功。中央流行疫情指揮中心昨公佈新增七宗確診病例，六宗境外輸入，一宗為入境台灣86天的比利時籍男子確診，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本土零確診紀錄恐破功<br />\n<br />\n指揮中心指揮官陳時中昨表示，編號案469的比利時籍工程師，為20多歲男性，今年5月3日入境到台，7月29日因欲返國，到醫院自費採檢，於昨日確診，惟迄今皆無症狀，現正住院隔離中。由於檢測後，其血清抗體IgM陰性、IgG強烈陽性，代表感染時間較早，有記者問該工程師是否屬本土個案，陳時中（圖）回應指感染源頭尚未判定。<br />\n<br />\n據指該工程師抵台後曾在台北一間旅館居家檢疫14天，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n台灣至昨日已逾110日零本土確診，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網"},{"pid":"28fd17677eda7e5cb779535713ad0a39b54b1584","tid":2136352,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T05:48:39.000Z","msg":"中共做野<br />\n新疆 香港 台灣"},{"pid":"bbeb5eaf2ba2220d9aa17cc7ebca3975e2074a91","tid":2136352,"uid":58958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T05:50:52.000Z","msg":"潛伏咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de8808ae63f961794d86c1c3d0b169e3476f10e","tid":2136352,"uid":130901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T05:53:04.000Z","msg":"諗起d神秘種子"},{"pid":"8377477be1e22fa486bf0c67e2608ede8b59bf9d","tid":2136352,"uid":73340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T05:57:59.000Z","msg":"隻病既潛伏期超屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多過60日完全無病徵<br />\n但周圍散毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無得守<br />\n呢獲要等疫苗先有得救"},{"pid":"7907adeac00134fa88b5acef8f228d33af8b225c","tid":2136352,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbeb5eaf2ba2220d9aa17cc7ebca3975e2074a91","tid":2136352,"uid":58958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T05:50:52.000Z","msg":"潛伏咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T05:58:45.000Z","msg":"得IgG 其實似佢未到台灣之前已經中咗好番 佢自己都唔知 只係台灣保險起見 計佢中咗"},{"pid":"045a73eafee902dc1bfe7958824a22c220b345fd","tid":2136352,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6de8808ae63f961794d86c1c3d0b169e3476f10e","tid":2136352,"uid":130901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T05:53:04.000Z","msg":"諗起d神秘種子"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T05:59:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as